_:Ne7240b0d4bed41de81f41846706a0886 <http://schema.org/description> "The National Space Operations Centre develops and operates the UK’s space surveillance and protection capabilities." <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:Ne7240b0d4bed41de81f41846706a0886 <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
_:Ne7240b0d4bed41de81f41846706a0886 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>NSpOC provides warning and protection services primarily to UK-licensed satellite operators and government departments.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"our-mission-sets-include\">Our mission sets include:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>protecting and defending the UK’s space interests</li>\n  <li>missile warning</li>\n  <li>uncontrolled re-entry early warning</li>\n  <li>in-space collision avoidance</li>\n  <li>fragmentation alerting and monitoring</li>\n  <li>support to licence monitoring</li>\n  <li>space weather notifications and advice</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Publicly available space weather notifications are provided by the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.metoffice.gov.uk/weather/learn-about/space-weather/met-office-role\" class=\"govuk-link\">Met Office</a>.</p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.monitor-your-satellites.service.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\">Monitor Your Satellites</a> is available to registered users (UK-licensed satellite operators)</p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
